11
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:27,506
<i>Bless the child of a workin' man</i>

12
00:01:27,588 --> 00:01:33,561
<i>She knows too soon who she is</i>

13
00:01:34,845 --> 00:01:39,521
<i>And bless the hands of a workin' man</i>

14
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:45,198
<i>He knows his soul is his</i>

