I have been known to cry.

1459
01:50:40,843 --> 01:50:42,766
- Well, what do you say?
- Ahhh...

1460
01:50:44,721 --> 01:50:46,268
Be happy.

1461
01:50:46,348 --> 01:50:48,271
Be well.

1462
01:50:48,350 --> 01:50:50,273
Same to you.

1463
01:50:56,233 --> 01:50:59,328
Best wishes don't
seem hardly enough.

1464
01:50:59,403 --> 01:51:00,871
I...

1465
